<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="股票管理,股票系统,股票分析,stock manager" />
    <meta name="description" content="个人持仓与盈亏记录工具" />
    <meta name="author" content="Stock Manager" />
    <meta name="referrer" content="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" />
    <title>Stock Manager - 股票管理系统</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="<%= context.config.publicPath %>favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <noscript>
      <div style="text-align: center; padding: 50px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
        <h1>需要启用 JavaScript</h1>
        <p>Stock Manager 需要 JavaScript 才能正常运行，请在浏览器设置中启用 JavaScript。</p>
      </div>
    </noscript>
    <div id="root">
      <style>
        html,
        body,
        #root {
          height: 100%;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
        }

        #root {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #eef2f8 100%);
        }

        .page-loading-container {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          height: 100%;
          min-height: 420px;
        }

        .page-loading-logo {
          width: 56px;
          height: 56px;
          margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .page-loading-spinner {
          padding: 24px 0;
        }

        .page-loading-brand {
          margin-top: 16px;
          font-size: 16px;
          color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
          font-weight: 500;
        }

        .page-loading-spinner .ant-spin-dot-item {
          position: absolute;
          display: block;
          width: 14px;
          height: 14px;
          background-color: #1677ff;
          border-radius: 50%;
          transform: scale(0.75);
          transform-origin: 50% 50%;
          opacity: 0.3;
          animation: antSpinMove 1s infinite linear alternate;
        }

        .page-loading-spinner .ant-spin-dot {
          position: relative;
          display: inline-block;
          width: 32px;
          height: 32px;
          font-size: 32px;
        }

        .page-loading-spinner .ant-spin-dot-item:nth-child(1) { top: 0; left: 0; }
        .page-loading-spinner .ant-spin-dot-item:nth-child(2) { top: 0; right: 0; animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .page-loading-spinner .ant-spin-dot-item:nth-child(3) { right: 0; bottom: 0; animation-delay: 0.8s; }
        .page-loading-spinner .ant-spin-dot-item:nth-child(4) { bottom: 0; left: 0; animation-delay: 1.2s; }
        .page-loading-spinner .ant-spin-dot-spin {
          transform: rotate(45deg);
          animation: antRotate 1.2s infinite linear;
        }

        @keyframes antSpinMove { to { opacity: 1; } }
        @keyframes antRotate { to { transform: rotate(405deg); } }
      </style>
      <div class="page-loading-container">
        <img
          src="<%= context.config.publicPath %>logo.svg"
          alt="Stock Manager Logo"
          class="page-loading-logo"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <div class="page-loading-spinner">
          <div class="ant-spin ant-spin-lg ant-spin-spinning">
            <span class="ant-spin-dot ant-spin-dot-spin">
              <i class="ant-spin-dot-item"></i>
              <i class="ant-spin-dot-item"></i>
              <i class="ant-spin-dot-item"></i>
              <i class="ant-spin-dot-item"></i>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-loading-brand">Stock Manager</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
